Made by Rexel259
Credits For Timer Prefab - Visual Timer / Counter - Fibbs
A little fun project that i thought i might attempt. it works well if you reach 10 points you get a M4. Any Bugs Glitchs i will fix in v2

Note -
      Button on the right starts the targets moving (move for 30 seconds)
      Button on the left resets the score counter after 30 seconds is up. to reset scores it must be pushed after 30 seconds are up.

Use the scout that came with the prefab for more of a challenge

Any Feed Back would be welcomed.
